OL,3,CSkye shooter Finlay MacDonald found
OL,4,Cguilty of murdering his brother-in-law
OL,6,FA father of four has been found guilty
OL,7,Fof the murder of his brother in law in
OL,8,Fa shooting rampage on the Isle of Skye
OL,9,Fin August 2022.
OL,11,FFinlay MacDonald, 41, was further
OL,12,Ffound guilty of three counts of
OL,13,Fattempted murder, including of against
OL,14,Fwife.
OL,16,FOn the morning of August, Finlay
OL,17,FMacDonald read texts on his wife's
OL,18,Fphone that he falsely believed showed
OL,19,Fshe was having an affair.
