OL,6,FThe court heard how the couple's
OL,7,Frelationship had broken down in recent
OL,8,Fmonths leading to arguments.
OL,10,FRowena MacDonald, 34, told the trial
OL,11,FFinlay MacDonald unfolded the knife as
OL,12,Fshe sat at the kitchen table and began
OL,13,Fusing it to attack her.
OL,15,FShe was asked where he stabbed her and
OL,16,Freplied: "Everywhere he could."
OL,18,FShe said: "I was absolutely terrified.
OL,19,FIt just kept coming and coming. I
OL,20,Fscreamed. The children came to the
OL,21,Fdoor from the living room and saw it."
