OL,6,FFinlay MacDonald said after stabbing
OL,7,Fhis wife in the kitchen he felt a
OL,8,F"total darkness come over me".
OL,10,FWhile Rowena lay bleeding in the
OL,11,Fdriveway of their home, Finlay
OL,12,FMacDonald proceeded to pack the car
OL,13,Fwith his gun, ammunition and a machete.
OL,15,FHe then drove 20 minutes to his
OL,16,Fsister's house, in the village of
OL,17,FTeangue.
OL,19,FLyn-Anne MacKinnon was unpacking her
OL,20,Fcar in the driveway when her brother
OL,21,Fdrove up.
