OL,6,FShe saw him walk inside with a gun in
OL,7,Fhand. Before Lyn-Anne had time to
OL,8,Ffollow him, she heard the sound of
OL,9,Fgunshots.
OL,11,FShe rushed inside at which point her
OL,12,Fhusband John MacKinnon collapsed in
OL,13,Fher arms. He died from the gunshot
OL,14,Fwounds.
OL,16,FThe 47 year old was a father of six.
OL,18,FMeanwhile Finlay MacDonald got in to
OL,19,Fhis car once again, driving a further
OL,20,F40 minutes to the house of his
OL,21,FOsteopath.
