OL,6,FMacdonald's wife Rowena told the High
OL,7,FCourt in Edinburgh that following
OL,8,Ftreatment with John Mackenzie,
OL,9,FMacDonald believed that his back pain
OL,10,Fwas much worse and added: "He told me
OL,11,Fthat he had ruined his life."
OL,13,FShe said: "He would frequently say, 'I
OL,14,Fam going to kill him, bloody kill him
OL,15,Ffor ruining my life."
OL,17,FEmergency services were by this point
OL,18,Faware of the ongoing incidents and a
OL,19,Fpatrol car spotted MacDonald's vehicle
OL,20,Fbefore he crossed the Skye bridge and
OL,21,Fon to the mainland.
