OL,6,FQuestions have been raised as to how
OL,7,FFinlay Macdonald was able to travel
OL,8,Fmore than 30 miles and carry out his
OL,9,Fattack over several hours without
OL,10,Fbeing stopped.
OL,12,FDavid Kennedy, General Secretary of
OL,13,Fthe Scottish Police Federation said:
OL,14,F"Years gone by police officers would
OL,15,Fhave had a firearm within the safe of
OL,16,Fthe police office.
OL,18,FWhen they would receive the call, they
OL,19,Fwould be allowed to go in to pick up
OL,20,Fthe gun and they were trained to use
OL,21,Fit.
